data.description: BEAUTIFUL, METICULOUSLY CARED FOR FIESTA MODEL. BUILT IN 2011, THIS 1994 SQ. FT. HOME FEATURES A SPACIOUS, OPEN FLOOR PLAN WITH 2 BEDROOMS, 21/2 BATHS, AND DEN/OFFICE.  Many upgrades including a gorgeous wrought iron security door that screens in the front entry.  Kitchen boasts quartz c/tops, designer backsplash, Blanco sink, gas stove, S/S appls., upgraded cabinets, pullouts, breakfast island, and dining area w/2' extension. Master bedroom has a bay window w/2' extension. Guest bedroom w/ensuite bathroom. Powder room across from spacious den. Large laundry room with cabinets & desk. Tandem garage with 4' extension, double sink, cabinets & workbench.  A full landscaped private rear yard w/paved patio, ramada and built in BBQ.  Great size, great floor plan.
